title: Al Ahli (KSA) vs Kawasaki (JPN) - AFC Champions League Elite 2024/25 - Final
description: Al-Ahli will face Kawasaki Frontale for the first time in the AFC Champions League elite and for the first time against a Japanese team. Conversely, this will be Kawasaki Frontales second encounter against a Saudi team after defeating Al-Nassr 3-2 in the semi-finals. Al-Ahli have won only once in 5 matches against East Asian teams, with the win against Shenzhen 2-1 in the 2005 quarter-finals. This will be the fourth final between a Saudi team and a Japanese team in the AFC Champions League elite, the most common final matchup in the tournament. All previous finals were between Al-Hilal and Urawa Red Diamonds, with Al-Hilal winning one title in 2019 and Urawa winning two titles in 2017 and 2

title: Special Coverage UCL Final Preview
description: The 2024/25 UEFA Champions League Final, featuring Paris Saint-Germain (PSG) and Inter Milan, is set to take place on Saturday, 31 May 2025, at the Allianz Arena in Munich, Germany. This match marks the first-ever European encounter between these two clubs. This final is particularly noteworthy as PSG aims to secure their first-ever Champions League title, while Inter seeks their fourth, having last won in 2010.
